{title: Bold Markup}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]This line has <b>bold text</b> in [C]it
[D]And <b>another bold phrase</b> [G]here
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]<b>The whole chorus line is bold</b>
[G]But this [D]one is [G]not
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[G]A single <b>word</b> can be bold
[C]Or <b>multiple words in a row</b> can [G]too
{end_of_verse}
